summary: This document is an email chain between Assistant United States Attorneys in the Southern District of New York discussing a premises search warrant. The focus is on paragraph 15 of the warrant, which states a phone was located at the 'Subject Premises,' defined as a 156-acre property including all structures, with pictures provided.
keyFacts: A premises search warrant was executed, targeting a 156-acre property defined as the 'Subject Premises'.
Paragraph 15 of the warrant states that a phone was located at the Subject Premises.
The warrant bundle included pictures of all structures on the 156-acre property.
The communication is between Assistant United States Attorneys in the Southern District of New York regarding the search warrant details.
